DevConnector Project

Day 1:
- Installed Nodejs, Vscode, postman and other necessary applications and dependencies for the project.
- Mongodb database on cloud.mongodb.com
- initialized git using 'git init'
- initialized package.json using 'npm init'
- Installed different packages
    1) express
    2) express-validator for validation
    3) bcryptjs - for password encryption
    4) config - for global variables
    5) gravatar - to pull avatar if available online
    6) jsonwebtoken - for token based validation
    7) mongoose - easier access to mongodb
    8) request - easier access to github repo
- Installed development packages (only used during development)
    1) nodemon - to get upto date server response
    2) concurrently - to run the frontend and backend all in 1 terminal easily